1. How to create another account in ubuntu
sudo adduser <UserName>
$ sudo adduser guest

2. How to add the root user in ubuntu

3. How to change the password of an account in ubuntu
sudo passwd <Username>
$ sudo passwd guest

4. create a directory
mkdir <DirectoryName>
$ mkdir test

5. remove a directory
rmdir <DirectoryName>
$ rmdir test

6. copy a file
cp <source file> <destination file>
$ cp source.txt destination.txt

7. rename a file
mv <source file> <destination file>
$ mv source.txt destination.txt

